definition: to appear/to arise/to emerge/to show up

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc
variant of 出[chu1] (classifier for plays or chapters of classical novels)
to appear/present/now/existing/current
to reappear

sentences.english: Non-codependent love requires wholeness to emerge within.
sentences.chinese: 不再相互依赖的爱，需要从内在出现完整。

sentences.english: Her arms showed green patches, indicating heavy internal bleeding.
sentences.chinese: 她的胳膊出现了青斑，表明有严重的内出血。

sentences.english: Our service is free repairs due to a series of bar code barriers.
sentences.chinese: 我们的服务是免费维修条码机出现一系列的障碍问题。

sentences.english: If there are chaos in the society, your planning cannot precede them.
sentences.chinese: 人道没有出现祸乱的时候，不可先策划兴师。

sentences.english: There'sno need for that kind of language in this magazine .
sentences.chinese: 这份杂志没必要出现那种语言。

sentences.english: As the saying goes, the devil often appears in the subtle.
sentences.chinese: 俗话说，魔鬼常出现在细微处。

sentences.english: These elements can be sorted, or processed in the order they appear.
sentences.chinese: 可以对这些元素排序，或以其出现的顺序处理它们。

sentences.english: But for now, a symbolic moment is about to occur.
sentences.chinese: 但在眼下，一个象征性的时刻即将出现。

sentences.english: He shows up in other people and what they say to you.
sentences.chinese: 他以其他人的形式出现，这些人对你说什么？

sentences.english: So the chemo finished. Then, blood began to appear in the patient's urine.
sentences.chinese: 后来，化疗结束以后，病人出现了血尿。

sentences.english: Some glorious morn--but when? Ah, who shall say?
sentences.chinese: 光荣的黎明，谁能说何时出现？

sentences.english: The image of the woman popped into his head out of the blue.
sentences.chinese: 那个女人的形象突然出现在他的脑海里。

sentences.english: Set the debug option to enable a backtrace when a; problem occurs.
sentences.chinese: 当有问题出现显示错误信息，便于调试。

sentences.english: Conclusion The above procedure is necessary for the ankle sprains with the injury of the common peroneal nerve.
sentences.chinese: 结论踝扭伤出现腓总神经损伤者应作探查松解减压术。

sentences.english: When the terminal has an alarm, the terminal will automatically transmit the location information to the management center.
sentences.chinese: 终端出现警情时，终端自动将位置信息传给管理中心。

sentences.english: But the dollar's unity or reunification of the rentier war is inevitable.
sentences.chinese: 但是美元统一或食利者的统一战争，是必然出现。
